---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 7, 2026';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Monumenth Growth"
  description="The terms that apply when you use this site or work with Monumenth Growth."
>
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground">
      These terms cover this website and the services Monumenth Growth provides to kitchen &
      bath remodeling contractors. By using this site or working with us, you agree to them.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">What we do</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Monumenth Growth turns raw project footage into short-form content and operates a
      WhatsApp-based lead funnel on your behalf. The specific scope, deliverables, pricing, and
      any guarantee for your project are agreed with you directly over WhatsApp before work
      begins — not on this page.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Your footage, your ownership</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Footage you send us stays yours. We use it to produce content and marketing assets on your
      behalf under the terms we agree with you. We don't resell or repurpose your footage for
      any other client.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">No guaranteed results on this page</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Marketing outcomes depend on factors outside our control, including your market, pricing,
      and responsiveness to leads. Any specific guarantee we offer will be stated in writing to
      you directly, not implied by anything on this site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Acceptable use</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Don't use this site to send unlawful, abusive, or fraudulent messages through our WhatsApp
      channel. We reserve the right to end a conversation or engagement that misuses it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Changes</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      We may update these terms as the business grows. Changes take effect when posted here.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Questions</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Message us on WhatsApp using the button on this site and we'll answer directly.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
